quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,aik dosray ko samnay dekh rahay hon ge ( is roz ) gunehgaar khwahish kere ga ke kisi terhan is din ke azaab ke badlay mein ( sab kuch ) day day yani apne betay
  70,12,aur apni biwi aur apne bhai
  70,13,aur apna khandan jis mein woh rehta tha
  70,14,aur jitne aadmi zameen mein hain ( gharz ) sab ( kuch day day ) aur apne tain azaab se churra le
  70,15,( lekin ) aisa hargiz nahi hoga woh bharakti hui aag hai
  70,16,khaal udhair daalnay wali
  70,17,un logon ko apni taraf bulaye gi jinhon ne ( deen haq se ) aaraazkiya
  70,18,aur ( maal ) jamakiya aur band kar rakha
  70,19,kuch shak nahi ke ensaan kam hosla peda howa hai
  70,20,jab usay takleef pahunchti hai to ghabra uthta hai
  70,21,aur jab asayish haasil hoti hai to bukheel ban jata hai
  70,22,magar namaz guzaar
  70,23,jo namaz ka iltazam rakhtay ( aur bilanagha parhte ) hain
  70,24,aur jin ke maal mein hissa muqarrar hai
  70,25,( yani ) mangnay walay ka. aur nah mangay walay wala ka
  70,26,aur jo roz jaza ko sach samajte hain
  70,27,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ke azaab se khauf rakhtay hain
  70,28,be shak un ke perwar-digaar ka azaab hai hi aisa ke is se be khauf nah howa jaye
  70,29,aur jo apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  70,30,magar apni biwion ya londion se ke ( un ke paas jaane par ) inhen kuch malamat nahi
  70,31,aur jo log un ke siwa aur ke khawastgah hon woh hadd se nikal jaane walay hain
  70,32,aur jo apni amanaton aur iqraron ka paas karte hain
  70,33,aur jo apni sh_hadton par qaim rehtay hain
  70,34,aur jo apni namaz ki khabar rakhtay hain
  70,35,yahi log baghaye bahisht mein izzat wa karam se hon ge
  70,36,to un kafiroon kokiya howa hai ke tumhari taraf doray chalay atay hain
  70,37,aur ) dayen baen se giroh giroh ho kar ( jama hotay jatay hain )
  70,38,kiya un mein se har shakhs yeh tawaqqa rakhta hai ke Nemat ke baagh mein daakhilkiya jaye ga
  70,39,hargiz nahi. hum ne un ko is cheez se pedakiya hai jisay woh jantay hain
